abstract: OTTAWA, Ontario, Sept. 17.--The box shook manufacturers here are in considerable trouble over their inability to ship shooks manufactured by them to the United States. abstract: NEW-BRUNSWICK, N.J., Sept. 17.--Thomas Patton of Perth Amboy was lodged in jail here today for shooting his wife. abstract: MONCTON, New-Brunswick, Sept. 22.--Calvin Du Binson and his wife, who live in a settlement called Catamount, in Kent County, went to call on a neighbor last evening, leaving their three children in the house.
